Multivariate linear regression analysis was employed to explore the behavioral significance of the IFC networks (3dRegAna, AFNI). The statistical threshold was set at p < 0.01 (3dClustSim corrected, cluster level α < 0.05, κ > 220, cluster size > 5940 mm3). The multivariate linear regression analysis shown in the following equation was employed [31]:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
